robots will be able to run up to a person's doorstep to deliver their package."SOURCES: TechCrunch, Continental AG, https://techcrunch.com/2019/01/07/robot-delivery-dogs-deployed-by-self-driving-cars-are-coming/?utm_source=tcfbpage&sr_share=facebookhttps://www.continental-corporation.com/en/press/press-releases/ces2019-157096***]]></description>
